---
title: Sweet Soy Mushroom & Pepper Tacos with Creamy Sweet Chili Slaw & Crispy Fried Onions
description: What are ’shrooms doing in a taco, you ask? Everything, we say! These fabulous funghi are the perfect way to make taco night meatless (and just as satisfying). Creminis and bell pepper are simmered with a soy glaze, turning them deliciously sweet and savory. And with the help of some seriously satisfying toppings—tangy sweet chili slaw, lime-marinated cucumber, and crispy fried onions—this recipe packs everything you could ever want inside steamy tortillas.
